        Gets a list of Agent Activities Each item on the list shows one agent's evaluation activity comprised of the number of evaluations and the highest, average, and lowest standard and critical scores, as well as a sub list showing the number and average score of evaluations for each evaluator for that agent. evaluatorUserId, startTime, and endTime are all filtering criteria. If no agent selection criteria are specified but an evaluatorUserId is, then the returned activity will be only for those agents that had evaluations where the evaluator is the evaluatorUserId.
